General.Name: Apex Equity Holdings Bhd
General.Description: Apex Equity Holdings Berhad, an investment holding company, engages in trading of marketable securities primarily in Malaysia. The company operates through four segments: Investment Holdings and Others, Stock and Futures Broking, Property Holdings and Property Development, and Money Lending. It also operates as a broker and dealer for stocks, shares, futures, and other securities. In addition, the company is involved in the investment, development, and holding of properties; underwriting and placement of securities; and nominee, share custodian, and investment advisor services. It serves institutional and retail clients. Apex Equity Holdings Berhad was incorporated in 1990 and is headquartered in Petaling Jaya, Malaysia.
